text: Uppalapati is an Indian surname and may refer to: * Prabhas (born as Uppalapati Venkata Satyanarayana Prabhas Raju, 1979), Indian actor * Uppalapati Surya Narayana Raju (died 2010), Telugu producer * Krishnam Raju (born as Uppalapati Venkata Krishnam Raju, 1940), Indian actor and politician * Uppalapati Narayana Rao (born 1958), Indian director, screenwriter, scriptwriter, actor and producer
title: Uppalapati
